// CreateSessionDialog
// Modal dialog for creating a new collab session. Collects session name, type
// (structured/vibe), and whether to enable the Browser UI renderer.

FUNCTION CreateSessionDialog(onClose, onConfirm) -> JSX                EXPORT
  Manages name, type (structured|vibe), and useRenderUI boolean state.
  Keyboard: Enter confirms if both name and type are set; Escape closes.
  Session type options: "structured" (guided phases) and "vibe" (freeform).
  Browser UI checkbox toggles useRenderUI.

---

FUNCTION handleConfirm() -> void
  Calls onConfirm(name, type, useRenderUI) only if both name and type are set.

---

FUNCTION handleKeyDown(e) -> void
  Enter -> handleConfirm. Escape -> onClose.
